sentence: In early trading on Friday, shares of Intel Corp ( INTC ) topped the list of the day's best performing Dow Jones Industrial Average components, trading up 3.9%.
Year to date, Intel Corp has lost about 1.5% of its value.
And the worst performing Dow component thus far on the day is Walmart ( WMT ), trading up 0.2%.
Walmart is lower by about 0.1% looking at the year to date performance.
Two other components making moves today are Procter & Gamble Company ( PG ), trading up 0.2%, and Caterpillar ( CAT ), trading up 3.1% on the day.
